<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ride-v">ride <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /raɪd/    美 /raɪd/  </p>
<p>(rode, ridden) vi &amp; vt</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>骑 (马等)；乘 (车等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>ride on</strong> a motorcycle / horse 
骑摩托车/马</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ride in / on a train 
乘火车</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ride an elevator 
乘电梯</p></div></div>